20Approach%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%0A%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3EFOI%20requests%20are%20filed%20under%20the%20%3Cstrong%3EFreedom%20of%20Information%20Act%202000%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20(UK).%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3Cli%3EResponses%20belong%20to%20the%20public%2C%20we%20aim%20to%20publish%20the%20documents%20we%20receive.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3Cli%3EPersonal%20data%20or%20information%20outside%20FOI%E2%80%99s%20scope%20(e.g.%20classified%20security%20matters)%20cannot%20be%20obtained.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3Cli%3ERestore%20Britain%20will%20ensure%20all%20requests%20are%20worded%20responsibly%2C%20fact-checked%2C%20and%20compliant%20with%20the%20law.%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3C%2Ful%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%26nbsp%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EImportant%20Notes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%0A%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3ESubmitting%20an%20FOI%20suggestion%20does%20not%20guarantee%20we%20will%20file%20it.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3Cli%3EWe%20do%20not%20share%20the%20identity%20of%20individuals%20who%20submit%20suggestions.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3Cli%3ERestore%20Britain%20does%20not%20provide%20legal%20advice%20on%20FOI%20rights%20for%20individuals.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20file%20a%20personal%20FOI%20yourself%2C%20you%20should%20contact%20the%20public%20authority%20directly.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3Cli%3EAll%20submissions%20are%20handled%20in%20line%20with%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fassets.nationbuilder.com%2Frestorebritain%2Fpages%2F530%2Fattachments%2Foriginal%2F1765191445%2FWhistleblower_Privacy___Protection_Policy.pdf%3F1765191445%22%3EWhistleblower%20Privacy%20%26amp%3B%20Protection%20Policy%20%2F%20Data%20Policy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20explains%20how%20we%20process%20and%20safeguard%20personal%20data%20under%20UK%20GDPR.%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3C%2Ful%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%26nbsp%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20style%3D%22font-weight%3A%20400%3B%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESubmit%20your%20FOI%20suggestion%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Frestorebritain.typeform.com%2FFOI-re